uiEntry.title: button_visible_mode
uiEntry.tooltip: Press this button to cycle through the different chat modes||The default behaviour is to fade out the chat when not in use. When it is locked, the chat stays on screen. When it is locked the chat won't automatically appear.

uiEntry.title: button_send_chat
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent( Address ) local parent = UIComponent( this:Parent("multiplayer_chat") )
function OnShortcut(f, ended) parent:InterfaceFunction("OnSendChat") end
